4-Piece Deluxe Age-Proof Haircare System - The System
Value:
Cleanse, condition, protect and nourish! This 4-step haircare system is designed to help restore shine, strength, volume, bounce and elasticity as it revitalizes the scalp for younger-looking hair.

Our Strengthening Shampoo helps replenish hydration while restoring hair’s strength, elasticity and resilience. The Smooth & Shiny conditioner is formulated with a natural silk protein known to double hair shine and amaranth extract for increased gloss and bounce. For softer, more manageable hair and smoother ends, apply the Styling and Protecting Spray to wet or dry hair. It detangles, tames frizz and shields hair from heat up to 450°F.

Thicker, fuller, stronger-looking hair begins at the scalp. Our invigorating Restorative Scalp Treatment features melon super antioxidants and our exclusive Melon Leaf Stem Cell Technology to help nourish hair follicles and replenish vital amino acids — creating the right environment for beautiful, healthy-looking hair.

No sulfates added. Safe for color-treated hair.

Display Name: 4-Piece Deluxe Age-Proof Haircare System - The System
4-Piece Deluxe Age-Proof Haircare System - The System

Value: Our luxurious Crème de Sérum delivers the benefits of both a serum and a cream, because it is both. The unique formulation contains peptides, hyaluronic acid and soluble collagen that together help increase moisturization and the look of firmness. Our melon super antioxidants help protect the skin from environmental aggressors. The result is moisturized, radiant, firmer-looking and feeling skin. Excellent for overnight use.

The delicate under-eye area is often the first to show signs of aging such as dryness, fine lines and wrinkles, dark circles, puffiness and a loss of vibrance. This Eye Enhancing Serum replenishes the under-eye area with moisture and helps reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. It has a lightweight, refreshing serum texture and combines peptides with antioxidants to improve the appearance of the area while helping prevent future damage from environmental aggressors.

Formulated to work together, this system cleanses, hydrates, protects, visibly firms the under-eye area and addresses signs of aging on your skin. When used consistently, you'll see visibly smoother, firmer, more hydrated and more luminous skin as well as a visible decrease in lines and wrinkles. Using this system morning and evening gives your skin the essentials it needs for younger-looking, more radiant skin.

This advanced formula now features Rètimel, a proprietary blend of melon super antioxidants and retinol plus a unique combination of amino acids that boosts skin's resilience for effective yet gentle results. This intensely moisturizing cream improves the look of wrinkles, ﬁne lines, skin discolorations and skin texture.

As we age, cell turnover slows down, so skin needs more exfoliation to get that look of youthful radiance. Dr. Sebagh created this multi-tasking 3-in-1 exfoliating treatment to combine the three most powerful exfoliating techniques for an ultimate at-home facial.

This treatment uses papaya enzymes, silica beads and glycolic acid to smooth texture and reveal more radiant skin. In addition, four types of French clay purify and detoxify skin. When skin is exfoliated regularly, the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles is also diminished.

Modern day living requires a multi-tasking moisturizer. This Anti-Aging Day Crème is specifically formulated to visibly plump, firm and hydrate your skin while providing SPF 30 protection from daily environmental aggressors that can lead to the visible signs of premature aging. Our multi-benefit cream contains hyaluronic acid to help keep skin supple and peptides that visibly reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, enhancing the look of smooth, plump, youthful skin.

This 4-in-1 primer detangles, conditions, smooths, protects hair from heat up to 450°F, and reduces frizz by 80% for up to 72 hours — even in high humidity. Hair needs this protection from everyday styling to feel strong, healthy and soft. Vegetable proteins strengthen hair and conditioning agents like panthenol add softness and shine.

Our bi-phase (oil & water) formula with Activated-C Technology keeps vitamin C stable and fresh, optimizing its absorption and potency. The oil phase also contains squalane to help prevent moisture loss for softer, more supple skin. The water phase houses a brightening complex of amino acids and niacinamide to provide an additional radiance boost. A synergy is achieved when the product is shaken and the ingredients are temporarily combined to create an active oil that brightens and evens skin tone as it hydrates and visibly firms and tightens skin.
